		<!-- First -->
			<section id="first" class="main">
				<header>
					<div class="container">
						<h2>Upwards crowdsources and clusters data to elicit more effective policymaking and development efforts </h2>

						<p>	
						Upwards brings together data from around the world on past and ongoing developmental efforts of all types and scopes. Upwards then performs state of the art machine learning algorithms to uncover latent structures and similarities between these efforts. With this knowledge base of past experience and insight, local leaders, policymakers, and changemakers can be much more successful in solving the developental problems at hand. </p>
					</div>
				</header>
				<div class="content dark style1 featured">
					<div class="container">
						<h1 style = "font-size: 20px; text-align: center;"> </h1>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="4u 12u(narrow)">
								<section>
									<span class="feature-icon"><span class="icon fa-line-chart"></span></span>
									<header>
										<h3>Learn</h3>
									</header>
									<p> Get data about both completed and ongoing efforts similar to the one you are working on. We use clustering algorithms to find projects that worked on a similar task and occured in the closest developmental initial context (economic state, population level, social capital, etc) to your own. e Learn what made projects similar successful</p>
								</section>
							</div>
							<div class="4u 12u(narrow)">
								<section>
									<span class="feature-icon"><span class="icon fa-bolt"></span></span>
									<header>
										<h3>Share</h3>
									</header>
									<p> Share data and details about a developmental effort you are involved it so that other people can make use of experience and reach out to you. In doing so, you open up your project to recieve feedback and experience from Upwards users, and also gain the ability to access premium data sources and analysis </p>
								</section>
							</div>
							<div class="4u 12u(narrow)">
								<section>
									<span class="feature-icon"><img style = "width: 300px;" src = "images/get-involved-top.png"></span>
									<header>
										<h3>Get Involved</h3>
									</header>
									<p>Find ongoing developmental projects nearby your location which you can contribute to, or find people who can contribute to your own effort. Scholars from across the world can provide guidance and insight on niche developmental efforts</p>
								</section>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="12u">
								<footer>
									<a href="#second" class="button scrolly">Learn more about the concept</a>
								</footer>
							</div>
						</div>
